dataSource

protected DataSource dataSource()
Description copied from class: IbatisSpringTxMethodRule
Can be overriden in subclasses and should return a data source. The default implementation of this method returns a data source for in-memory H2 database. This method retuns different data sources if it is invoked in different threads (database name contains hash code of the current thread).
